# --- Tenant isolation (per-agency private working areas) ---
# Per master plan §3.3: meta.json + practice-scenario/ + submission-package/
# remain trackable on client/* branches. The patterns below catch raw inbox,
# structured intake, and Claude-Design workspace — none of these should ever
# land on main.
agencies/*/_inbox/**
agencies/*/intake/**
agencies/*/workspace/**
